<paragraph blockId="7.[160,1156,1530,1693]" pageId="7" pageNumber="2599">
The first mtDNA barcodes for the species are presented here (
<accessionNumber box="[907,1021,1599,1623]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/LR738835" pageId="7" pageNumber="2599">LR738835</accessionNumber>
, 
<accessionNumber box="[1033,1147,1599,1623]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/LR738833" pageId="7" pageNumber="2599">LR738833</accessionNumber>
). The species varies at least by 6.6% genetic distance (654bp CO1 barcode) from the most similar Bornean congener 
<taxonomicName authority="Freitag &amp; Molls &amp; Bouma &amp; Garces &amp; Rossato &amp; Cosentino &amp; Delledonne, 2019" authorityName="Freitag &amp; Molls &amp; Bouma &amp; Garces &amp; Rossato &amp; Cosentino &amp; Delledonne" authorityYear="2019" box="[456,651,1668,1693]" class="Insecta" family="Elmidae" genus="Grouvellinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="2599" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigerquadratus" status="sp. nov.">
