<bibRefCitation author="Freitag H &amp; Pangantihon CV &amp; Njunjic I" box="[848,1053,1357,1381]" pageId="8" pageNumber="2600" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref11421" refString="Freitag H, Pangantihon CV, Njunjic I. 2018. Three new species of Grouvellinus Champion 1923 (Insecta, Coleoptera, Elmidae) from Maliau Basin, Sabah, Borneo, discovered by citizen scientists during the first Taxon Expedition. Zookeys. 751: 1 - 21. doi: 10.3897 / zookeys. 754.24276" type="journal article" year="2018">Freitag et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
